      • MARKUP_FRAME

        static final java.lang.String MARKUP_FRAME
        Markup for describe the main frame
        • name : Name of the class (With the package name) [Mandatory]
        • title : Frame title [Optional]
        • layout : Layout class to use in {JHelpBorderLayout (Default value), JHelpHorizontalLayout, JHelpVerticalLayout, JHelpTableLayout} [Optional]

      • MARKUP_BACKGROUND_ROUND_REACTANLGE

        static final java.lang.String MARKUP_BACKGROUND_ROUND_REACTANLGE
        Markup for describe a background component with round rectangle shape. It must contains a component as sub_markup
        • name : Name of the component [Mandatory]
        • arc : Arc size (Default 20) [Optional]
        • background : Background color in hexadecimal (AARRGGBB) (Default 80808080) [Optional]
        See Also:

        • name : Name of the component [Mandatory]
        • space : Empty space (Default 10) [Optional]
        • background : Background color in hexadecimal (AARRGGBB) (Default 80808080) [Optional]
